.Dd May 16, 2004
.Dt FCU 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm fcu
.Nd Apple cfu fan controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "fcu* at maciic?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the Apple FCU
fan controller.
The device controls and monitors fans found in some Apple
machines. 
These values are made available through the
.Xr sysctl 8
interface.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr maciic 4 ,
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr sensorsd 8 ,
.Xr sysctl 8
